Class LifetimeRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uwo.csd.cs2212.team13.LifetimeRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class LifetimeRecord
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    LifetimeRecord is a simple Java object that represents the lifetime totals and the rules that govern access to and updates of this data.
